Name: Reclaimer 2954 Ship Showdown Poster
Description: Celebrate the Reclaimer, Aegis Dynamics' industrial salvage ship, making the final four of the 2954 Ship Showdown with this poster. Equipped with a reinforced cargo bay, a long-range jump drive and launch pods for unmanned drones, the Reclaimer is an ideal ship for taking advantage of deep space wrecks.
